---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <main class="flex flex-col w-full bg-custom-light-white">
    <Navbar />

    {
      // Hero Section //
    }

    <section
      id="about"
      class="bg-custom-light-white flex md:flex-row flex-col md:justify-between md:items-center md:m-auto md:max-w-[70%]"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col md:w-[50%] gap-4 md:p-0 p-4">
        <span class="md:text-4xl text-3xl font-bold"
          >Hello. I am Aditya Jyoti.</span
        >
        <span class="md:text-2xl text-xl"
          >A die hard engineer looking forward to breaking open things and then
          never being able to put them back together. <br /> I also code sometimes.</span
        >

        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aditya-jyoti/" target="_blank">
          <div class="relative">
            <div
              class="absolute z-10 bg-custom-light-grey border-2 border-black w-fit p-2 font-bold hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-150"
            >
              Connect With Me
            </div>
            <div
              class="absolute z-0 bg-custom-black border-2 border-black w-fit p-2 font-bold translate-x-1 translate-y-1"
            >
              Connect With Me
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <img
        src="/img-small.png"
        alt="profile"
        class="flex ml-auto md:hidden w-64 -mt-14"
      />
      <img src="/img-long.png" alt="profile" class="md:flex hidden" />
    </section>

    {
      // interests mobile //
    }

    <section class="md:hidden relative flex flex-col w-full">
      <div class="border-t-2 border-black w-full"></div>

      <div
        class="flex gap-4 absolute w-full items-center justify-center -top-5 font-semibold"
      >
        <div
          class="bg-custom-light-grey p-1 border-2 border-black w-28 text-center"
        >
          roboticist
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-custom-light-grey p-1 border-2 border-black w-28 text-center"
        >
          programmer
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-custom-light-grey p-1 border-2 border-black w-28 text-center"
        >
          elocutionist
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {
      // Interests //
    }
    <div
      class="w-full -mb-5 z-10 -mt-5 md:flex hidden items-center justify-center"
    >
      <div
        class="border-2 border-black w-fit py-1 px-12 bg-custom-light-grey text-lg font-bold tracking-widest"
      >
        interests
      </div>
    </div>

    <section
      class="bg-custom-light-grey border-y-2 border-black w-full h-full py-2 px-14 hidden md:flex"
    >
      <div class="flex mt-4 mb-4">
        {
          // interest 1
        }

        <div class="flex flex-col w-[80%] text-center">
          <span class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wide">robotics</span>
          <span>
            I love building things from scratch. Imagine a world where all the
            hardware that you use was sourced and built by yourself. That's the
            world I want to live in. As a part of a special team dedicated to
            robotics in my college, I hope to develop my skills further and take
            part in competitions around the world.
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="border-r-2 border-black mx-4"></div>

        {
          // interest 2
        }

        <div class="flex flex-col w-[80%] text-center">
          <span class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wide">programming</span>
          <span>
            Programming feels like magic to me. It gives me the freedom to
            explore and build my own world with only my imagination as a limit.
            I hope to be able to make a product that helps easen the lives of
            people that use it and be able to make a difference in the world.
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="border-r-2 border-black mx-4"></div>

        {
          // interest 3
        }

        <div class="flex flex-col w-[80%] text-center">
          <span class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-wide"
            >public speaking</span
          >
          <span>
            The rush of emotions i feel when I am on stage, talking to a crowd
            is something I can not explain. Seeing everyone's eyes on me,
            listening to my every word and so much more gives me more adrenaline
            than any thing in the world. I hope to one day be able to address
            the peopl if only for a moment.
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {
      // projects
    }

    <section class="w-[80%] mx-auto py-4 mt-2">
      <span class="text-3xl font-bold">Projects</span>

      <div
        class="flex md:flex-row flex-col md:gap-0 gap-8 md:justify-between mt-4"
      >
        {
          // project 1
        }

        <div>
          <div
            class="absolute z-0 bg-black border-2 border-black w-[21rem] h-[21rem] translate-x-2 translate-y-2"
          >
          </div>

          <div
            class="relative z-10 bg-custom-dark-white border-2 border-black w-[21rem] h-[21rem]"
          >
            <div
              class="border-b-2 border-black py-1 px-2 flex gap-2 bg-custom-grey"
            >
              <i class="fa-regular fa-circle bg-custom-light-white rounded-full"
              ></i>
              <i class="fa-regular fa-circle bg-custom-light-white rounded-full"
              ></i>
              <i class="fa-regular fa-circle bg-custom-light-white rounded-full"
              ></i>
            </div>

            <img
              src="/proj1.jpg"
              alt="project 1"
              class="h-28 w-full border-b-2 border-black"
            />
            <div class="p-2 flex flex-col gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">Recruitment Site</span>

              <span class="text-sm">
                Production ready recruitment website featuring a rich home page
                and an easy to navigate form filling section. The project
                includes a custom api to fetch all submissions and display them
                for the admin to view inside of the website itself.
              </span>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-2 flex items-end">
              <a href="#" class="">
                <div
                  class="bg-custom-grey px-8 border-2 border-black w-fit ml-2 font-bold hover:bg-custom-light-grey"
                >
                  visit
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {
          // project 2
        }

        <div>
          <div
            class="absolute z-0 bg-black border-2 border-black w-[21rem] h-[21rem] translate-x-2 translate-y-2"
          >
          </div>

          <div
            class="relative z-10 bg-custom-dark-white border-2 border-black w-[21rem] h-[21rem]"
          >
            <div
              class="border-b-2 border-black py-1 px-2 flex gap-2 bg-custom-grey"
            >
              <i class="fa-regular fa-circle bg-custom-light-white rounded-full"
              ></i>
              <i class="fa-regular fa-circle bg-custom-light-white rounded-full"
              ></i>
              <i class="fa-regular fa-circle bg-custom-light-white rounded-full"
              ></i>
            </div>

            <img
              src="/proj2.jpg"
              alt="project 2"
              class="h-28 w-full border-b-2 border-black"
            />
            <div class="p-2 flex flex-col gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">Custom Shell</span>

              <span class="text-sm">
                A simple custom shell written in c++ which performs all the
                basic tasks that any normal shell would do. It can cd into
                directories, make them, remove them, rename then and more.
                Currently need to add more features like a text editor etc.
              </span>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-2 flex items-end">
              <a
                href="https://github.com/aditya-jyoti/custom-shell"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <div
                  class="bg-custom-grey px-8 border-2 border-black w-fit ml-2 font-bold hover:bg-custom-light-grey"
                >
                  visit
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {
          // project 3
        }

        <div>
          <div
            class="absolute z-0 bg-black border-2 border-black w-[21rem] h-[21rem] translate-x-2 translate-y-2"
          >
          </div>

          <div
            class="relative z-10 bg-custom-dark-white border-2 border-black w-[21rem] h-[21rem]"
          >
            <div
              class="border-b-2 border-black py-1 px-2 flex gap-2 bg-custom-grey"
            >
              <i class="fa-regular fa-circle bg-custom-light-white rounded-full"
              ></i>
              <i class="fa-regular fa-circle bg-custom-light-white rounded-full"
              ></i>
              <i class="fa-regular fa-circle bg-custom-light-white rounded-full"
              ></i>
            </div>

            <img
              src="/proj3.jpg"
              alt="project 3"
              class="h-28 w-full border-b-2 border-black"
            />
            <div class="p-2 flex flex-col gap-2">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold">Introduce Yourself</span>

              <span class="text-sm">
                A sample project where you can open up PRs to make your first
                open source contribution, introducing yourself to other people
                who are starting out as well. Your introductions will then be
                publically visible on the <a
                  href="https://aditya-jyoti.github.io/Introduce-Yourself/"
                  target="_blank"
                >
                  <strong>website</strong>
                </a>.
              </span>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-2 flex items-end">
              <a
                href="https://github.com/aditya-jyoti/Introduce-Yourself"
                target="_blank"
              >
                <div
                  class="bg-custom-grey px-8 border-2 border-black w-fit ml-2 font-bold hover:bg-custom-light-grey"
                >
                  visit
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full flex justify-end mt-8">
        <div class="">
          <div
            class="absolute z-0 bg-black w-fit font-bold px-8 py-1 border-2 border-black translate-x-1 translate-y-1"
          >
            See More
          </div>
          <a href="https://github.com/aditya-jyoti" target="_blank">
            <div
              class="relative z-10 bg-custom-grey w-fit font-bold px-8 py-1 border-2 border-black hover:translate-x-0.5 hover:translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-150"
            >
              See More
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {
      // project 3
    }
  </main>
</Layout>
